GSD.description:
net: sched: sfb: fix null pointer access issue when sfb_init() fails

This is an automated ID intended to aid in discovery of potential security vulnerabilities. The actual impact and attack plausibility have not yet been proven.
This ID is fixed in Linux Kernel version v6.0.6 by commit 723399af2795fb95687a531c9480464b5f489333, it was introduced in version v2.6.39 by commit e13e02a3c68d899169c78d9a18689bd73491d59a. For more details please see the references link.
